1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:08,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:04,000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:11,140
[Episode 25]

5
00:01:13,750 --> 00:01:14,500
I'm going to decoct medicinal herbs.

6
00:01:17,110 --> 00:01:18,090
Aren't you going to save him?

7
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:24,730
I can't die yet.

8
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:28,940
But he values you more than his own life!

9
00:01:29,940 --> 00:01:30,530
And you?

10
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:35,530
You're just a coward who fears death.

11
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:36,810
What's wrong with wanting to live?

12
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:38,810
Don't you want to live?

13
00:01:41,270 --> 00:01:42,580
If you don't even cherish your own life,

14
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:44,620
what's the point of living?

15
00:01:46,940 --> 00:01:47,530
Yes.

16
00:01:49,270 --> 00:01:51,420
The Flower Fairy willingly gave herself for the Demon Lord.

17
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:53,420
And yet, life after life,

18
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:55,340
they still end in the same cycle of death.

19
00:01:55,910 --> 00:01:57,290
The dead go peacefully,

20
00:01:57,310 --> 00:01:58,250
without a care.

21
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,810
But what about the living?

22
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,010
You wouldn't understand.

23
00:02:06,750 --> 00:02:08,900
Watching the most important person die before your eyes

24
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:11,220
and even

25
00:02:12,900 --> 00:02:14,340
sending them off yourself

26
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,410
is utter despair.

27
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:22,020
After Lu died,

28
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:24,570
Xiuyuan barely survived.

29
00:02:25,990 --> 00:02:28,690
With me by his side, we sheltered each other from the storms.

30
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,220
And now,

31
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:33,340
you want him to devour me?

32
00:02:34,590 --> 00:02:37,090
When he wakes up, how will he live with himself?

33
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:42,300
I don't know if you want him to live,

34
00:02:43,430 --> 00:02:44,810
or die, or

35
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:47,370
suffer in between.

36
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:53,130
I won't let him face any of this.

37
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,570
But this is your fate.

38
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:56,850
I don't believe in fate!

39
00:02:58,110 --> 00:02:58,970
My master said

40
00:02:59,870 --> 00:03:00,940
nothing in this world

41
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,340
is set in stone or forced.

42
00:03:03,110 --> 00:03:04,090
There is only what I want.

43
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,410
What matters is the choice you make.

44
00:03:07,870 --> 00:03:09,570
I want to stay alive with Xiuyuan,

45
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:12,020
so I'll find a way for us both

46
00:03:12,110 --> 00:03:13,020
to make it.

47
00:03:14,670 --> 00:03:16,570
What if you can't change it?

48
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:21,370
If it comes down to it, we'll die together.

49
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:22,570
No big deal!

50
00:03:41,390 --> 00:03:41,940
Lifei!

51
00:03:46,390 --> 00:03:47,090
You're awake.

52
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:48,340
What happened

53
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:50,500
last night?

54
00:03:53,670 --> 00:03:54,410
Nothing.

55
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:57,370
Drink your medicine. Sit down.

56
00:03:58,830 --> 00:04:00,500
Later, we'll go set up a stone for Master.

57
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,090
He liked to sleep.

58
00:04:02,550 --> 00:04:04,410
Let's pick a spot where the sun shines every day.

59
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:09,060
Lifei.

60
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:11,740
Don't overthink. We'll figure things out.

61
00:04:12,550 --> 00:04:13,340
Drink your medicine.

62
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:18,980
Okay.

63
00:04:24,590 --> 00:04:26,620
You dare drink what this wretch gives you?

64
00:04:28,030 --> 00:04:28,740
Master?

65
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,860
Don't get me started. What have you two done?

66
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:33,620
Cuixuan

67
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:35,570
mistook you for demon spies.

68
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:37,330
He's making us bring you back

69
00:04:37,350 --> 00:04:38,570
to verify your identities.

70
00:04:39,230 --> 00:04:40,570
I'm the one connected to demons,

71
00:04:40,790 --> 00:04:41,500
not Lifei.

72
00:04:42,350 --> 00:04:44,180
Take me instead.

73
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:44,620
You...!

74
00:04:45,030 --> 00:04:46,540
Guangwei, I'm begging you.

75
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,500
Please don't be angry.

76
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:49,660
I'm begging you.

77
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:55,330
Look at Xiuyuan. He is already this sick.

78
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:59,450
You really think they can get away?

79
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,860
- They... they actually got away.
- You...

80
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,180
Look what you've done!

81
00:05:10,470 --> 00:05:12,010
Then we'll find them again.

82
00:05:18,390 --> 00:05:19,500
There are vines under this cliff.

83
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:21,540
Go down to Ganhua Realm and wait for me.

84
00:05:21,710 --> 00:05:22,620
I'll draw them off.

85
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,420
What are you doing?

86
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:45,210
Xiuyuan, don't let the demon take you!

87
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:46,300
Listen to your master!

88
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:47,540
Live well.

89
00:05:50,390 --> 00:05:51,210
Lei Xiuyuan!

90
00:05:52,030 --> 00:05:53,420
You self-righteous scumbag!

91
00:05:54,080 --> 00:05:55,810
Why do you always act on your own?

92
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,620
Why do you give up?

93
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:11,890
Guangwei.

94
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,100
He's the best disciple

95
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,450
you've ever had.

96
00:06:15,910 --> 00:06:17,060
Your own disciple!

97
00:06:22,150 --> 00:06:23,500
Don't be too rough on him.

98
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:26,500
I'll go find my disciple.

99
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:30,300
Lifei! Lifei!

100
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:33,860
Lifei!

101
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,570
Lifei!

102
00:06:38,230 --> 00:06:41,250
Xiuyuan, you really know demonic arts?

103
00:06:41,830 --> 00:06:42,770
Where did you learn them?

104
00:06:43,350 --> 00:06:46,210
Was it from the Outcast Tomb at White Cliff?

105
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:49,940
I am an outcast too. From across the sea.

106
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,250
Impossible!

107
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:55,010
At Chufeng Academy, I probed your spirit root.

108
00:06:55,710 --> 00:06:57,370
You're truly made of flesh and blood.

109
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,300
Master, you've never crossed the sea.

110
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:03,060
How do you know outcasts don't have flesh and blood?

111
00:07:03,230 --> 00:07:03,810
Shut your mouth!

112
00:07:06,350 --> 00:07:07,860
I've seen those outcasts.

113
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:10,860
They're all bloodthirsty beasts and demons.

114
00:07:11,270 --> 00:07:12,330
They're not human!

115
00:07:15,030 --> 00:07:17,980
Just because we look and act

116
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:18,810
differently from you,

117
00:07:19,270 --> 00:07:20,330
we're not human?

118
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:32,180
Are you telling me

119
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:37,130
that the one I poured my heart into teaching

120
00:07:37,910 --> 00:07:40,060
is the very enemy the Central Plains sects

121
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:42,860
despise most?

122
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,330
Master.

123
00:07:57,320 --> 00:08:00,130
But the way of the world dictates that the rigid breaks first.

124
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,250
Only Wuyue Court's techniques

125
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:05,540
balance rigidity with flexibility. And that is what lasts.

126
00:08:06,390 --> 00:08:07,660
Would you like to join Wuyue Court?

127
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:09,860
Yes.

128
00:08:12,910 --> 00:08:15,740
The rigid breaks first. Balance rigidity with flexibility.

129
00:08:16,710 --> 00:08:19,450
Master, thank you for taking me in and teaching me.

130
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:22,100
I will never forget it.

131
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:33,690
I'm a terrible disciple. Please take back your gift, Master.

132
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,850
You were taught by me.

133
00:08:40,920 --> 00:08:44,060
I can't let you become a great threat to the immortal sects!

134
00:08:54,830 --> 00:08:55,730
Master.

135
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,180
Master.

136
00:09:23,540 --> 00:09:24,540
Master.

137
00:09:39,230 --> 00:09:41,140
You... Soul bewitching?

138
00:10:04,420 --> 00:10:08,450
Sir, thank you for helping the Lord sever his worldly ties

139
00:10:08,990 --> 00:10:10,140
and return to our clan.

140
00:10:10,470 --> 00:10:11,540
Lifei!

141
00:10:14,180 --> 00:10:16,020
Guangwei, I couldn't find Lifei.

142
00:10:21,300 --> 00:10:22,020
Where's Xiuyuan?

143
00:10:38,830 --> 00:10:39,660
No response.

144
00:10:40,920 --> 00:10:41,810
He should be fine.

145
00:10:55,990 --> 00:10:57,330
What is Qingcheng to you?

146
00:11:00,980 --> 00:11:04,180
At East Sea's Mount Man, the vast ocean stretches endlessly.

147
00:11:04,830 --> 00:11:07,810
Left together by Qingcheng of Wuyue Court and Riyan of Qingqiu.

148
00:11:16,750 --> 00:11:17,780
So my master

149
00:11:19,060 --> 00:11:20,210
is Qingcheng.

150
00:11:42,470 --> 00:11:46,060
The Demon Lord was fierce and unstoppable with the Divine Tree's power.

151
00:11:47,100 --> 00:11:48,730
With my friend Riyan's help,

152
00:11:49,230 --> 00:11:51,730
I severed his horns and dealt a heavy blow to his forces.

153
00:12:04,060 --> 00:12:06,240
I used the Senluo Grand Art to stop the Demon Lord

154
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,180
from destroying the Divine Tree.

155
00:12:07,470 --> 00:12:08,940
But Yecha reverted to an infant form.

156
00:12:09,230 --> 00:12:11,090
Only a faint trace of the Divine Tree's fruit remained.

157
00:12:11,300 --> 00:12:14,180
Yet even a blade of grass deserves life. I resolved to devote my life

158
00:12:14,420 --> 00:12:18,180
to studying this being and finding a solution to the Sea Calamity.

159
00:12:29,750 --> 00:12:30,780
For a century after that,

160
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:33,140
Riyan and I traveled across countless lands,

161
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:35,450
but never discovered the source of the Sea Calamity.

162
00:12:35,660 --> 00:12:37,210
Because the spirit energy across the sea is thin,

163
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:39,140
Yecha's green fruit couldn't grow.

164
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:41,540
And we were badly wounded from our battle with Yecha,

165
00:12:41,830 --> 00:12:44,140
and our cultivation had greatly diminished.

166
00:12:44,470 --> 00:12:45,570
So we returned to the Central Plains

167
00:12:45,750 --> 00:12:48,850
and went into seclusion in Riyan's homeland, Qingqiu.

168
00:14:24,470 --> 00:14:25,540
Decades later,

169
00:14:25,870 --> 00:14:28,260
the fruit that had remained unchanged finally awakened into a spirit.

170
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:30,420
Even the Ganhua Realm, with its ordinary spirit energy,

171
00:14:30,750 --> 00:14:32,420
was enriched by it.

172
00:14:32,870 --> 00:14:35,330
After more than 300 years in Qingqiu,

173
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:37,810
on the twenty-fifth day of the twelfth month in the Year of Gengwu, at midnight,

174
00:14:38,110 --> 00:14:40,900
the shell suddenly cracked open, and inside was a newborn girl.

175
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:43,900
Radiant and naturally gifted.

176
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:46,780
She was human, and yet not human.

177
00:15:01,870 --> 00:15:03,140
This girl was born of heaven itself.

178
00:15:04,100 --> 00:15:06,540
Her own spirit energy could generate endless spirit energy.

179
00:15:07,630 --> 00:15:09,540
She could also absorb the spirit energy of others.

180
00:15:10,230 --> 00:15:11,210
If used well,

181
00:15:12,510 --> 00:15:14,420
she could help us boost our cultivation

182
00:15:14,990 --> 00:15:16,210
and make us invincible.

183
00:15:18,820 --> 00:15:22,300
But this reborn Divine Tree was no different from a mortal child.

184
00:15:23,220 --> 00:15:24,730
To keep her from falling back into calamity,

185
00:15:25,340 --> 00:15:27,730
I decided to raise her myself.

186
00:15:33,340 --> 00:15:36,940
But Yecha had a peculiar fondness for her, and I feared

187
00:15:37,350 --> 00:15:38,380
old sins would resurface.

188
00:15:39,350 --> 00:15:41,810
So I set three interlocking seals upon her

189
00:15:42,100 --> 00:15:42,970
and sent her away.

190
00:15:43,590 --> 00:15:44,850
With these seals,

191
00:15:45,700 --> 00:15:46,900
they would hold each other in check.

192
00:15:47,230 --> 00:15:49,970
If kept apart in this life, they could break free from fate.

193
00:15:50,710 --> 00:15:51,690
It's foolproof.

194
00:15:53,420 --> 00:15:56,140
Forget the past. Stay away from conflict.

195
00:15:57,820 --> 00:15:59,570
Just live as an ordinary person.

196
00:16:19,590 --> 00:16:21,690
Mr. Lei of Gaolu was a dear friend of mine.

197
00:16:22,580 --> 00:16:24,330
I set up a protective formation for Gaolu,

198
00:16:24,830 --> 00:16:27,420
and he promised to keep this child safe.

199
00:16:41,060 --> 00:16:42,940
But I grow old, and my strength fades.

200
00:16:43,940 --> 00:16:45,730
Time passes and never returns.

201
00:16:46,830 --> 00:16:48,810
Though I may live long as an immortal,

202
00:16:49,220 --> 00:16:50,690
I long to return to my homeland.

203
00:16:51,340 --> 00:16:52,970
Cultivation is hindered by worldly attachments.

204
00:16:53,420 --> 00:16:55,060
You're meant to rise above mortal ties

205
00:16:55,230 --> 00:16:56,180
and achieve the Great Dao.

206
00:16:56,980 --> 00:16:59,610
Yet now you're held captive by this being.

207
00:17:00,110 --> 00:17:01,810
You've cared for her so painstakingly.

208
00:17:02,300 --> 00:17:03,140
You're seeing her

209
00:17:03,180 --> 00:17:04,660
as a real person.

210
00:17:05,220 --> 00:17:05,770
Do you really

211
00:17:06,360 --> 00:17:08,580
want her to live as an ordinary person forever?

212
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:12,730
What's wrong with being ordinary?

213
00:17:13,120 --> 00:17:14,580
My Xiaobangchui is so lovely.

214
00:17:15,070 --> 00:17:16,380
Even if she can do nothing, it doesn't matter.

215
00:17:16,420 --> 00:17:17,660
I'll protect you. Right?

216
00:17:17,750 --> 00:17:18,940
Your Xiaobangchui?

217
00:17:19,310 --> 00:17:20,770
You know that no matter how human she seems,

218
00:17:20,940 --> 00:17:22,690
she's still just the Fruit of the Divine Tree.

219
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:24,730
I've placed seals in her sea of mind.

220
00:17:25,270 --> 00:17:26,100
If you don't tell her,

221
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:27,970
she'll never know.

222
00:17:28,220 --> 00:17:28,690
You...!

223
00:17:30,700 --> 00:17:31,730
Stubborn.

224
00:17:32,550 --> 00:17:33,290
Fool.

225
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:36,290
What good is brilliance and talent?

226
00:17:36,790 --> 00:17:37,730
In the end,

227
00:17:38,360 --> 00:17:40,100
you're still tied down by this burden.

228
00:17:40,700 --> 00:17:41,970
You can hide it from her for a day, a year,

229
00:17:41,990 --> 00:17:42,770
even a century,

230
00:17:43,220 --> 00:17:45,010
but how can you hide it from her for a lifetime?

231
00:17:45,420 --> 00:17:46,420
As long as I live,

232
00:17:47,420 --> 00:17:48,530
I'll protect her.

233
00:17:50,940 --> 00:17:51,820
My mind is made up.

234
00:17:52,620 --> 00:17:53,580
Don't try to change it.

235
00:18:03,900 --> 00:18:05,580
I used to live on Hushe Peak.

236
00:18:05,940 --> 00:18:07,290
Everyone said it looked like a mallet.

237
00:18:07,620 --> 00:18:08,250
You

238
00:18:08,660 --> 00:18:10,100
are Xiaobangchui.
[*Sounds like "little mallet"]

239
00:18:17,220 --> 00:18:18,770
The Divine Tree brims with natural spirit energy.

240
00:18:19,230 --> 00:18:20,420
Without external spirit energy input,

241
00:18:20,940 --> 00:18:22,250
it draws out spirit energy on its own.

242
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:26,340
The spirits around Qingqiu were all drawn to it and purified.

243
00:18:32,710 --> 00:18:33,450
Don't be afraid.

244
00:18:33,700 --> 00:18:34,530
But when she was three,

245
00:18:34,990 --> 00:18:36,100
a calamity struck,

246
00:18:36,220 --> 00:18:38,180
and her innate spirit energy suddenly vanished.

247
00:18:38,310 --> 00:18:40,140
She became no different from an ordinary child,

248
00:18:40,470 --> 00:18:41,770
unable to channel any spirit energy.

249
00:18:42,510 --> 00:18:43,530
All these peculiarities

250
00:18:43,620 --> 00:18:45,770
were hidden within this ordinary girl.

251
00:18:45,940 --> 00:18:47,860
Since I treated the child as my own,

252
00:18:47,900 --> 00:18:49,210
Riyan worried my attachments

253
00:18:49,470 --> 00:18:50,770
would block my cultivation recovery.

254
00:18:51,230 --> 00:18:53,580
He repeatedly urged me to teach her the way of cultivation.

255
00:18:53,710 --> 00:18:54,860
I always refused.

256
00:18:54,990 --> 00:18:55,730
In a fit of anger,

257
00:18:56,030 --> 00:18:57,730
Riyan left Qingqiu.

258
00:19:05,460 --> 00:19:06,620
It's fine if you can't do it.

259
00:19:07,230 --> 00:19:09,420
You could just be my disciple.

260
00:19:09,750 --> 00:19:10,820
A girl

261
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:13,490
spending her days fighting isn't proper.

262
00:19:14,470 --> 00:19:16,420
Making braised radish for me

263
00:19:16,460 --> 00:19:17,210
is the real business.

264
00:19:17,310 --> 00:19:17,970
Am I right?

265
00:19:18,700 --> 00:19:20,380
I'm dirt poor.

266
00:19:20,620 --> 00:19:22,010
If I raised you like a proper girl,

267
00:19:22,700 --> 00:19:24,100
we'd starve.

268
00:19:26,270 --> 00:19:26,900
Let's go.

269
00:19:27,790 --> 00:19:30,180
We'll go make some money.

270
00:19:30,180 --> 00:19:33,500
[Infallible Divination]

271
00:19:33,510 --> 00:19:34,420
Let's go!

272
00:19:34,460 --> 00:19:35,450
Sir, I'll have a baozi.

273
00:19:35,470 --> 00:19:35,940
Sure.

274
00:19:35,980 --> 00:19:37,050
Xiaobangchui, are you hungry?

275
00:19:37,990 --> 00:19:40,380
I'll buy you something to eat.

276
00:19:40,420 --> 00:19:41,380
Sir, would you like a baozi?

277
00:19:41,420 --> 00:19:42,490
Two, please.

278
00:19:42,710 --> 00:19:43,250
This one.

279
00:19:43,790 --> 00:19:44,290
Here.

280
00:19:45,230 --> 00:19:46,100
This one.

281
00:19:47,360 --> 00:19:48,210
Careful. It's hot.

282
00:20:01,840 --> 00:20:04,970
The girl was clever and sharp. It brought me great comfort.

283
00:20:05,600 --> 00:20:06,730
But all these peculiarities

284
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:09,140
would make her life restless.

285
00:20:09,600 --> 00:20:11,250
So I gave everything I had

286
00:20:11,600 --> 00:20:13,250
to protect her for life.

287
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:42,490
I thought if I concealed her spirit aura

288
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:43,860
and hid her among the mortals,

289
00:20:44,340 --> 00:20:46,010
we'd have nothing to worry about.

290
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:49,210
But heaven had other plans.

291
00:20:50,100 --> 00:20:51,050
Over a decade later,

292
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:54,340
she crossed paths with an old enemy she was never meant to see again.

293
00:20:55,990 --> 00:20:57,380
Knowing my cover was blown

294
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:58,860
and I could no longer protect her,

295
00:20:59,340 --> 00:21:00,620
I quickly sent word to Riyan.

296
00:21:01,160 --> 00:21:03,250
Fearing it was too late, I left a hurried note

297
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:05,580
for Xiaobangchui to go to Chufeng Academy

298
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:07,770
and seek my other disciple, Hu Jiaping.

299
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:09,100
At the academy,

300
00:21:09,550 --> 00:21:11,730
with Jiaping and my old friend Zuo Qiu watching over her,

301
00:21:12,200 --> 00:21:13,970
perhaps she and the Yecha boy

302
00:21:14,470 --> 00:21:15,940
wouldn't repeat the same ill-fated bond.

303
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:20,450
Master, food's ready.

304
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:26,690
Master!

305
00:21:26,710 --> 00:21:29,010
I couldn't bear to leave the girl behind.

306
00:21:29,510 --> 00:21:30,250
Master!

307
00:21:30,270 --> 00:21:30,940
But

308
00:21:31,270 --> 00:21:33,250
Cuixuan's tracking talisman had caught up.

309
00:21:33,840 --> 00:21:34,690
Master!

310
00:21:47,440 --> 00:21:48,770
Cuixuan claimed to be severely wounded

311
00:21:49,270 --> 00:21:51,420
and invited me to meet him at Hushe Peak.

312
00:21:52,470 --> 00:21:55,530
I walked into his trap and was captured.

313
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:09,900
Qingcheng.

314
00:22:11,470 --> 00:22:12,530
Where is the Divine Tree?

315
00:22:15,880 --> 00:22:17,010
There is

316
00:22:18,230 --> 00:22:19,770
no Divine Tree in this world.

317
00:22:21,750 --> 00:22:23,620
As a disciple of Wuyue Court,

318
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:25,770
you side with those across the sea

319
00:22:26,070 --> 00:22:27,250
and cozy up to monsters.

320
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:29,010
You even built the Outcast Tomb.

321
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:30,100
Tell me,

322
00:22:30,710 --> 00:22:32,860
where have you hidden the Divine Tree?

323
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:42,770
In this life, I was tied down by worldly attachments

324
00:22:43,070 --> 00:22:44,290
and never achieved the Great Dao.

325
00:22:44,840 --> 00:22:48,420
My only wish is that Xiaobangchui can live as an ordinary person,

326
00:22:49,230 --> 00:22:50,450
[Senluo Grand Art]
happy and free

327
00:22:50,790 --> 00:22:52,380
for all her days.

328
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:54,450
Master,

329
00:22:56,440 --> 00:22:57,380
with you gone,

330
00:22:58,990 --> 00:23:00,290
how can I be happy?

331
00:23:08,070 --> 00:23:09,250
Without killing Cuixuan,

332
00:23:10,710 --> 00:23:12,340
I don't deserve freedom.

333
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:19,010
I want supreme power.

334
00:23:20,750 --> 00:23:22,250
I don't want my loved ones

335
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,900
dying in front of me again.

336
00:23:27,310 --> 00:23:28,050
Master,

337
00:23:29,550 --> 00:23:31,380
I will avenge you.

338
00:23:47,790 --> 00:23:52,290
Follow your will. One thought moves all things.

339
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:55,450
Scatter into wind, gather into form.

340
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:57,340
Draw the essence of heaven and earth,

341
00:23:57,470 --> 00:24:00,380
and fuse the five elemental powers of metal, wood, water, fire, and earth.

342
00:24:15,620 --> 00:24:18,450
Let the universe reverse. Let all creation revive.

343
00:25:08,920 --> 00:25:09,660
It's done.

344
00:25:26,840 --> 00:25:27,770
Still not quite there.

345
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:34,450
With the full strength of our clan,

346
00:25:35,340 --> 00:25:37,860
we'll help the Lord restore his power,

347
00:25:38,230 --> 00:25:41,450
break the curse, and sweep through all immortal sects!

348
00:25:47,340 --> 00:25:51,100
The heart divides yin and yang; a single thought dictates the world.

349
00:26:13,840 --> 00:26:21,690
Save us!

350
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:22,580
I'm not...

351
00:26:23,200 --> 00:26:23,940
I'm not Yecha!

352
00:26:24,990 --> 00:26:25,860
How can I save you?

353
00:26:26,510 --> 00:26:27,380
Save us, My Lord!

354
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:30,580
- Save us! - Save us!

355
00:27:01,600 --> 00:27:02,690
Where the heart finds peace,

356
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:08,580
there is home.

357
00:27:10,070 --> 00:27:11,180
Master Qingcheng?

358
00:27:11,880 --> 00:27:14,100
Resentment is a net, trapping both user and prey.

359
00:27:14,470 --> 00:27:17,010
Only by breaking free can the soul find peace.

360
00:27:23,750 --> 00:27:24,420
Master Qingcheng!

361
00:27:30,750 --> 00:27:31,340
Remember,

362
00:27:32,440 --> 00:27:33,730
where your heart leads

363
00:27:34,310 --> 00:27:36,290
is the right choice for you.

364
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:42,210
Who am I?

365
00:27:43,840 --> 00:27:44,970
Where is my heart leading?

366
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:47,900
Xiuyuan. You're Lei Xiuyuan!

367
00:27:58,070 --> 00:27:58,660
Remember,

368
00:27:59,440 --> 00:28:00,690
where your heart leads

369
00:28:01,840 --> 00:28:03,770
is the right choice for you.

370
00:28:33,510 --> 00:28:36,770
Is she wounded and unconscious, or has she gone berserk?

371
00:28:56,440 --> 00:28:57,180
Qin Yangling,

372
00:28:57,840 --> 00:28:59,620
you've been practicing demonic arts just like Zong Quan?

373
00:29:01,960 --> 00:29:03,180
What demonic arts?

374
00:29:03,680 --> 00:29:04,900
As long as it makes me stronger,

375
00:29:05,270 --> 00:29:06,530
who dares say anything?

376
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:15,140
You can devour spirits too?

377
00:29:18,440 --> 00:29:19,140
Let me go!

378
00:29:25,470 --> 00:29:26,250
Lifei.

379
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:29,450
Back at Chufeng Academy,

380
00:29:29,710 --> 00:29:31,730
I truly treated you well.

381
00:29:40,160 --> 00:29:41,900
Thank you.

382
00:30:09,510 --> 00:30:10,290
Master.

383
00:30:14,030 --> 00:30:15,100
Cuixuan.

384
00:30:15,880 --> 00:30:16,900
Die!

385
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:24,140
Overestimating yourself.

386
00:30:39,750 --> 00:30:41,010
You really are the Divine Tree.

387
00:30:42,360 --> 00:30:44,050
You've hidden it well.

388
00:30:44,510 --> 00:30:45,860
You ruined my master's life.

389
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:48,250
Is the Divine Tree really that important?

390
00:30:49,790 --> 00:30:52,530
With the power of the Divine Tree,

391
00:30:52,790 --> 00:30:54,420
I can unite all the immortal sects.

392
00:30:55,510 --> 00:30:57,340
When the Sea Calamity opens the passage,

393
00:30:58,470 --> 00:31:02,180
I'll conquer the lands across the sea

394
00:31:02,790 --> 00:31:04,820
and wipe out the demon outcasts.

395
00:31:05,310 --> 00:31:07,900
This is the righteous path of the immortal sects.

396
00:31:08,120 --> 00:31:09,100
Righteous path?

397
00:31:09,510 --> 00:31:10,450
It's all nonsense!

398
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:15,420
What is this?

399
00:31:16,310 --> 00:31:16,900
How is it?

400
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:21,100
My dragon-trapping lock and spirit-binding seal.

401
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:22,940
Feels good, doesn't it?

402
00:31:23,400 --> 00:31:25,380
You used these to imprison my master?

403
00:31:26,470 --> 00:31:28,530
You two are truly master and disciple.

404
00:31:29,070 --> 00:31:30,010
Be patient.

405
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:32,490
I'll make you suffer

406
00:31:32,680 --> 00:31:34,690
everything your master did.

407
00:31:57,400 --> 00:31:58,180
It's useless.

408
00:31:59,030 --> 00:32:03,100
I've fused the powers of the lock and the seal.

409
00:32:04,360 --> 00:32:05,420
No one but me

410
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:07,450
can undo it.

411
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:12,620
Cui-Cuixuan,

412
00:32:12,990 --> 00:32:14,450
even if Lifei has done wrong,

413
00:32:14,750 --> 00:32:16,660
we should bring her back to Wuyue Court.

414
00:32:17,030 --> 00:32:18,490
We can question her properly there.

415
00:32:18,640 --> 00:32:19,210
Alright?

416
00:32:19,710 --> 00:32:20,970
The evidence is clear.

417
00:32:21,750 --> 00:32:22,940
What's there to question?

418
00:32:26,840 --> 00:32:28,250
Let go of my disciple!

419
00:32:29,270 --> 00:32:32,050
Chongyi! You dare shield a demon

420
00:32:32,070 --> 00:32:33,770
and defy Wuyue Court's rules?

421
00:32:33,960 --> 00:32:35,210
I stake my life

422
00:32:35,470 --> 00:32:36,620
that Lifei is no demon!

423
00:32:38,200 --> 00:32:39,340
Stubborn fool.

424
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:40,860
Cuixuan!

425
00:32:43,550 --> 00:32:44,140
Guangwei!

426
00:32:50,200 --> 00:32:51,180
Let's see

427
00:32:51,510 --> 00:32:52,490
who dares take my disciple

428
00:32:53,030 --> 00:32:54,770
while I'm here!

429
00:33:00,470 --> 00:33:01,860
Cuixuan, stop!

430
00:33:02,230 --> 00:33:02,970
Master!

431
00:33:06,960 --> 00:33:07,970
Don't protect me anymore.

432
00:33:10,160 --> 00:33:11,730
I am the Fruit of the Divine Tree.

433
00:33:29,510 --> 00:33:31,580
It was because the Demon Lord possessed the Divine Tree

434
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:34,820
that the Central Plains sects suffered such devastating losses.

435
00:33:35,120 --> 00:33:37,620
Now the Divine Tree has reappeared.

436
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:40,730
This thing must not fall into demon hands.

437
00:33:44,990 --> 00:33:46,900
Baifu, watch your words.

438
00:33:47,550 --> 00:33:49,140
What do you mean by "this thing"?

439
00:33:49,750 --> 00:33:51,180
Lifei is a living person.

440
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,380
She's a disciple of Zhuiyu Peak.

441
00:33:57,070 --> 00:33:58,380
You're an elder of Zhuiyu Peak,

442
00:33:58,680 --> 00:34:00,380
yet she's fooled you all this time!

443
00:34:01,200 --> 00:34:03,010
When she absorbed the Achillea Bead,

444
00:34:03,310 --> 00:34:04,450
I found it suspicious.

445
00:34:04,600 --> 00:34:06,820
But you defended her at every turn!

446
00:34:08,960 --> 00:34:10,780
Why bring up

447
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:12,130
the Achillea Bead again?

448
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:14,010
Lifei earned that Achillea Bead

449
00:34:14,030 --> 00:34:16,010
fair and square.

450
00:34:16,590 --> 00:34:18,780
Yes, she is the Divine Tree.

451
00:34:19,150 --> 00:34:19,940
But has she ever done

452
00:34:19,960 --> 00:34:22,010
anything harmful?

453
00:34:22,720 --> 00:34:25,420
Has she ever hurt any of the immortal sects?

454
00:34:25,590 --> 00:34:27,610
She colluded with demons, trespassed into the forbidden area,

455
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:28,650
and wounded Yangling!

456
00:34:28,920 --> 00:34:30,970
Every one of those is a violation!

457
00:34:31,400 --> 00:34:32,090
Besides,

458
00:34:33,670 --> 00:34:35,220
for the immortal sects of the Central Plains,

459
00:34:35,670 --> 00:34:36,780
the existence of the Divine Tree

460
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:38,010
is a great threat!

461
00:34:38,030 --> 00:34:40,380
You see her as a threat,

462
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:42,300
so you want to kill her.

463
00:34:42,590 --> 00:34:43,220
Is that it?

464
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:44,450
And

465
00:34:44,880 --> 00:34:46,300
you said she trespassed into the forbidden area.

466
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:47,570
I want to know

467
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:49,700
what exactly is hidden in the forbidden area

468
00:34:49,700 --> 00:34:50,900
of Hushe Peak!

469
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:54,010
Why did Lifei go to such lengths to break in?

470
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:05,490
She and Lei Xiuyuan

471
00:35:05,700 --> 00:35:07,450
are both demons from across the sea.

472
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:08,940
They posed as our disciples

473
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:11,260
to spy on our sect's secrets.

474
00:35:12,960 --> 00:35:15,450
Chongyi, you should know

475
00:35:16,550 --> 00:35:18,610
that the righteous and the demonic can't coexist.

476
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,700
If you continue to take her side

477
00:35:20,720 --> 00:35:21,700
and blur the lines,

478
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:24,450
don't blame me for being harsh.

479
00:35:25,150 --> 00:35:25,650
What,

480
00:35:26,800 --> 00:35:29,090
are you going to charge me with colluding with demons too?

481
00:35:32,700 --> 00:35:33,530
Fine.

482
00:35:34,030 --> 00:35:36,490
You've never liked Lifei or me anyway.

483
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:37,340
Might as well

484
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:39,610
lock us up together!

485
00:35:39,990 --> 00:35:41,970
That way, you won't have to keep guessing

486
00:35:41,990 --> 00:35:43,340
and finding faults with us!

487
00:35:43,630 --> 00:35:44,090
You...!

488
00:35:44,550 --> 00:35:45,530
Alright.

489
00:35:45,550 --> 00:35:46,420
Don't let an outcast

490
00:35:46,440 --> 00:35:47,530
damage our bonds.

491
00:35:48,150 --> 00:35:49,700
Let's detain the Divine Tree for now.

492
00:35:50,070 --> 00:35:51,450
We'll discuss what to do next.

493
00:35:53,700 --> 00:35:54,900
You're still injured.

494
00:35:55,670 --> 00:35:56,700
Let's not rush into this.

495
00:35:57,070 --> 00:35:58,300
We'll deal with this later.

496
00:36:00,920 --> 00:36:01,780
The Divine Tree has been captured.

497
00:36:02,510 --> 00:36:04,220
The demons won't let this rest.

498
00:36:05,590 --> 00:36:06,530
We must be on guard.

499
00:36:07,360 --> 00:36:10,450
I've ordered a restriction spell over Wuyue Shrine

500
00:36:10,590 --> 00:36:11,610
and sealed off all news.

501
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:17,530
But while the Divine Tree is detained,

502
00:36:17,990 --> 00:36:18,780
no one

503
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,970
is to approach Wuyue Shrine.

504
00:36:25,670 --> 00:36:26,220
Where's Dongyang?

505
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:28,530
Where is he?

506
00:36:29,110 --> 00:36:31,570
The day before, Dongyang received a letter from an old friend.

507
00:36:32,190 --> 00:36:33,740
He was invited on urgent business.

508
00:36:34,070 --> 00:36:35,170
He'll be back in a few days.

509
00:36:35,190 --> 00:36:36,570
The sect is in turmoil,

510
00:36:36,880 --> 00:36:38,610
yet he still has the mind for social visits?

511
00:36:39,280 --> 00:36:41,130
You've all gotten too comfortable.

512
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,780
You no longer know what matters!

513
00:37:16,700 --> 00:37:18,940
Lifeng was damaged

514
00:37:19,070 --> 00:37:20,170
and is hard to repair.

515
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:24,700
For now, all we can do is protect Mu's remaining spirit.

516
00:37:25,220 --> 00:37:27,610
We'll need to find a rare spirit-energy treasure

517
00:37:27,960 --> 00:37:29,900
to reforge her sword body.

518
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:33,010
Perhaps...

519
00:37:33,510 --> 00:37:34,450
Perhaps what, sir?

520
00:37:35,070 --> 00:37:36,090
You must save Mu.

521
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:36,940
She...

522
00:37:39,190 --> 00:37:39,820
Jiaping.

523
00:37:46,280 --> 00:37:48,300
Mu is a thousand-year-old artifact spirit.

524
00:37:50,070 --> 00:37:51,300
As long as she has a breath of life,

525
00:37:52,150 --> 00:37:53,450
there's still a chance to mend

526
00:37:53,840 --> 00:37:55,420
her primordial spirit and restore her body.

527
00:37:56,470 --> 00:37:57,420
As for you,

528
00:37:58,030 --> 00:37:59,130
you were wounded by Cuixuan.

529
00:37:59,720 --> 00:38:03,050
Your cultivation has dropped by at least forty percent.

530
00:38:04,990 --> 00:38:06,010
I was careless.

531
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:09,170
I never expected that Cuixuan's seclusion for healing

532
00:38:10,280 --> 00:38:12,380
was about collecting demon bones in the miniature realm,

533
00:38:13,320 --> 00:38:14,300
absorbing their lingering spirits,

534
00:38:14,760 --> 00:38:15,530
and taking them for himself.

535
00:39:19,150 --> 00:39:19,610
Let's go.

536
00:39:21,150 --> 00:39:25,170
Master Qingcheng was probably murdered.

537
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:30,610
Sir, I'll leave Mu in your care.

538
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:33,860
I'm going to Wuyue Court.

539
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:35,300
For Lifei?

540
00:39:35,440 --> 00:39:35,940
Yes.

541
00:39:36,470 --> 00:39:38,260
Lifei sent me a distant-sensing talisman from Qingqiu.

542
00:39:39,220 --> 00:39:41,130
She's probably been taken back to Wuyue Court by Cuixuan.

543
00:39:41,700 --> 00:39:43,340
Cuixuan has always wanted the Divine Tree all to himself.

544
00:39:44,150 --> 00:39:45,380
Lifei is in grave danger

545
00:39:45,550 --> 00:39:46,700
with him.

546
00:39:47,700 --> 00:39:49,090
I can't stand by and do nothing.

547
00:39:53,550 --> 00:39:55,860
Jiaping, with your injuries,

548
00:39:56,240 --> 00:39:57,740
you won't change a thing.

549
00:39:58,860 --> 00:40:00,010
You'd collapse

550
00:40:00,240 --> 00:40:02,820
before you even saved Lifei.

551
00:40:03,340 --> 00:40:04,260
Even if it kills me,

552
00:40:05,550 --> 00:40:06,900
I must protect Lifei.

553
00:40:08,070 --> 00:40:08,970
I've always known

554
00:40:08,990 --> 00:40:09,940
Lifei's true identity.

555
00:40:11,070 --> 00:40:12,450
But I clung to hope,

556
00:40:13,510 --> 00:40:14,740
choosing to hide and run away.

557
00:40:15,460 --> 00:40:17,300
I failed my master's trust.

558
00:40:18,630 --> 00:40:19,260
Jiaping,

559
00:40:20,470 --> 00:40:23,610
I hope you and Lifei

560
00:40:24,150 --> 00:40:25,860
can live on safely,

561
00:40:26,470 --> 00:40:27,820
unbound by past lives.

562
00:40:30,460 --> 00:40:31,780
Now the demons are running rampant.

563
00:40:32,900 --> 00:40:35,490
The immortal sects are in turmoil.

564
00:40:35,940 --> 00:40:36,940
Outrage is brewing everywhere.

565
00:40:37,720 --> 00:40:39,420
If we reveal the Divine Tree now,

566
00:40:40,630 --> 00:40:41,740
it won't end well.

567
00:40:45,510 --> 00:40:47,700
Since Cuixuan wants the Divine Tree for himself,

568
00:40:49,300 --> 00:40:51,130
let's make the news of its appearance

569
00:40:52,110 --> 00:40:53,380
known to all.

570
00:41:00,400 --> 00:41:00,970
Master,

571
00:41:01,240 --> 00:41:03,130
everyone's saying Lifei colluded with demons

572
00:41:03,150 --> 00:41:04,010
and is an outcast from across the sea.

573
00:41:04,940 --> 00:41:06,220
They're saying she should be tortured.

574
00:41:06,590 --> 00:41:07,530
Is any of it true?

575
00:41:11,380 --> 00:41:15,450
If Lifei really is an outcast,

576
00:41:16,670 --> 00:41:18,700
what will you do?

577
00:41:19,110 --> 00:41:21,340
Master, as long as you still claim her as your disciple,

578
00:41:21,630 --> 00:41:23,130
she'll always be our junior sister.

579
00:41:23,460 --> 00:41:23,940
Yeah.

580
00:41:24,300 --> 00:41:25,820
I trust Lifei's character.

581
00:41:26,190 --> 00:41:27,740
She would never harm the innocent

582
00:41:27,780 --> 00:41:28,900
or bring shame to you.

583
00:41:29,550 --> 00:41:30,610
Let's just break her out.

584
00:41:30,980 --> 00:41:32,170
Get her out first.

585
00:41:32,720 --> 00:41:35,380
With your skills? Break her out?

586
00:41:36,630 --> 00:41:40,420
If a fight breaks out, you'd be lucky to just defend yourselves.

587
00:41:40,820 --> 00:41:42,740
But we can't just sit back and do nothing.

588
00:41:43,240 --> 00:41:44,820
Qin Yangling is guarding Wuyue Shrine.

589
00:41:45,340 --> 00:41:47,010
What if he tries to get revenge?

590
00:41:47,670 --> 00:41:49,050
You're right.

591
00:41:50,980 --> 00:41:53,340
That scoundrel Qin Yangling

592
00:41:53,940 --> 00:41:55,780
is capable of anything.

593
00:42:01,420 --> 00:42:01,970
Master.

594
00:42:31,820 --> 00:42:33,940
On this mission, we must seize the Divine Tree's power

595
00:42:34,510 --> 00:42:35,860
and restore Dizang Sect's glory!

596
00:42:38,050 --> 00:42:38,780
[The Eternal Fragrance]

597
00:42:38,780 --> 00:42:40,560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

598
00:42:53,500 --> 00:42:57,020
♪The warmth within my arms♪

599
00:42:57,180 --> 00:43:00,700
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

600
00:43:00,820 --> 00:43:04,340
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

601
00:43:04,460 --> 00:43:07,940
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

602
00:43:07,940 --> 00:43:11,580
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

603
00:43:11,980 --> 00:43:15,260
♪I can no longer tell you♪

604
00:43:15,380 --> 00:43:18,900
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

605
00:43:18,940 --> 00:43:21,940
♪Utter that line♪

606
00:43:22,100 --> 00:43:24,140
♪Knowing love and hate♪

607
00:43:24,220 --> 00:43:28,620
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

608
00:43:29,340 --> 00:43:31,420
♪I still linger on♪

609
00:43:31,580 --> 00:43:35,860
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

610
00:43:36,020 --> 00:43:40,540
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

611
00:43:40,620 --> 00:43:44,140
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

612
00:43:44,220 --> 00:43:47,660
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

613
00:43:47,940 --> 00:43:51,180
♪I wish you well♪

614
00:43:51,340 --> 00:43:53,060
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

615
00:43:53,220 --> 00:43:57,900
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

616
00:43:58,500 --> 00:44:00,580
♪You're still screaming♪

617
00:44:00,740 --> 00:44:05,220
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

618
00:44:05,340 --> 00:44:09,820
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

619
00:44:10,060 --> 00:44:13,020
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

620
00:44:13,140 --> 00:44:15,020
♪Leaping straight into♪

621
00:44:15,140 --> 00:44:19,900
♪That heartbreaking past♪

622
00:44:20,140 --> 00:44:23,660
♪Just to keep you safe♪

623
00:44:30,100 --> 00:44:33,420
♪My breath is about to stop♪

624
00:44:33,540 --> 00:44:37,060
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

625
00:44:37,180 --> 00:44:40,620
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

626
00:44:40,780 --> 00:44:43,980
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

627
00:44:44,100 --> 00:44:47,820
♪I smile as it ends♪

628
00:44:47,980 --> 00:44:51,620
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

629
00:44:51,820 --> 00:44:55,220
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

630
00:44:55,380 --> 00:44:58,500
♪To light your way through the night♪

631
00:44:58,580 --> 00:45:00,620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

632
00:45:00,700 --> 00:45:05,100
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

633
00:45:05,860 --> 00:45:07,900
♪I still linger on♪

634
00:45:08,060 --> 00:45:12,340
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

635
00:45:12,500 --> 00:45:17,020
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

636
00:45:17,100 --> 00:45:20,300
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

637
00:45:20,500 --> 00:45:22,460
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

638
00:45:22,540 --> 00:45:26,940
♪I build a paradise♪

639
00:45:27,100 --> 00:45:30,580
♪To wander with you♪
